name: Green Eggs and Ham
overview: Guy-Am-I, an inventor, and his friend Sam-I-Am go on a cross-country trip that would test the limits of their friendship. As they learn to try new things, they find out what adventure brings.

episodes.name: Here
episodes.overview: Soon after a rare chickeraffe goes missing from the Glurfsburg Zoo, Sam and Guy meet by chance at a diner, setting off a series of extraordinary events.

episodes.name: Car
episodes.overview: Guy shows up to return Sam's briefcase, only to learn he's got company. Elsewhere, a mother-daughter duo begins a very slow drive through the desert.

episodes.name: Train
episodes.overview: With the Bad Guys in pursuit, Sam and Guy board a train to Meepville and meet Michellee, a cautious bean counter, and her thrill-seeking daughter, E.B.

episodes.name: Fox
episodes.overview: Taking a detour to find the chickeraffe some food, Guy and Sam cross paths with an egg-loving fox who's working hard to control his appetite.

episodes.name: Dark
episodes.overview: While seeking shelter for the night, the trio gets stuck in a junkyard. The only upside for an inventor like Guy? It's full of raw materials.

episodes.name: Box
episodes.overview: Panic hits the streets of Prinz Pazookle when the locals learn there's a chickeraffe in town. But a colorful carnival is bringing everyone together.

episodes.name: Mouse
episodes.overview: A singing rodent comes to the rescue in North Shvizelton when Sam and Guy wind up in jail with no real plan to get themselves out.

episodes.name: Rain
episodes.overview: To escape the Bad Guys -- and stormy weather -- Sam and friends spend the night in Michellee's cabin, but trouble follows. Snerz hires outside help.

episodes.name: Goat
episodes.overview: Guy and Sam need a next-level plan when Snerz's animal-napper chases them up a cliff. As for the Bad Guys, they're definitely down -- but not out.

episodes.name: House
episodes.overview: The fugitive friends make a stop in Stovepipe Junction, where Sam gets to meet Guy's family -- and reveals a shocking secret.

episodes.name: Boat
episodes.overview: Just as Guy's about to try a bite of breakfast, the Bad Guys bust in with the truth about their mission. Under the sea, the plot thickens.

episodes.name: There
episodes.overview: After a close call on the docks, Guy gets captured and learns he's been duped. Michellee gives her daughter a tour of Meepville.

episodes.name: Anywhere
episodes.overview: The SnerzDay Gala sets the stage for a surprise ending that's full of twists and turns -- and a heartwarming act of true friendship.

episodes.name: The Mom Identity
episodes.overview: A taste of home sends Sam on a mission to find his mom, with Guy and E.B. in tow. But a plot twist takes their story in a wildly different direction.

guest_stars.character: Joaquin Furmano / Smoothie Salesman / Cabbie Left (voice)
guest_stars.name: David Kaye

episodes.name: Tinker Tailor Mother Spy
episodes.overview: The friends hear the histories of Yookia and Zookia. Sam's desperate to connect with Pam, but a suspicious Guy doesn't trust her.

episodes.name: Goldenguy
episodes.overview: Sam shadows Pam on a super-secret spy mission, even though she'd rather work alone. In tech-loving Zookia, Guy finds an inventor's paradise.

episodes.name: Three Days of the Mom-dor
episodes.overview: Pam and Sam team up for an undercover job. A scampering squail leads E.B. to the top of the border wall, where she makes a mysterious new friend.

episodes.name: To Yookia With Love
episodes.overview: E.B. runs away to spend the day with Looka. Everything's perfect - until a hidden relic reveals the truth about the history of the wall.

episodes.name: You Only Mom Twice
episodes.overview: Sam and his mom track the Moo-Lacka-Moo to a tropical island crawling with surprises. Guy gets Michellee's message and can't believe his eyes.

episodes.name: Guyfall
episodes.overview: A well-meaning Guy saves E.B. from danger and shares his doubts about Pam with Sam - but it only seems to push them both further away from him.

guest_stars.character: Zook Guard 1 / Zook Guard 3 / Patrol Zook 1 (voice)
guest_stars.name: Herbert Siguenza

episodes.name: The Sam Who Came in From the Cold
episodes.overview: So who gets the Moo-Lacka-Moo? With the fate of Yookia and Zookia hanging in the balance, the friends must decide where their loyalties lie.

guest_stars.character: Zook Soldier 2 / Zook Guard / TV Announcer (voice)
guest_stars.name: Herbert Siguenza

episodes.name: On Her Dookess' Secret Service
episodes.overview: Pam is forced to pick sides as the Zooks and Yooks prepare for an all-out war. A quick-thinking Michellee is Guy's secret weapon.

episodes.name: The Mom Who Loved Me
episodes.overview: Butter side up, butter side down: The great butter battle is brewing! Can our heroes work together to stop it in time?
